<td class="content">
Have you already set up countries of delivery and divided them into regions, set up the shipping profile and defined shipping costs? Not yet? Return to <a href="/en/welcome/quick-start/quick-start-shipping-options">setting up shipping options</a>.
</td>
</tr>
