<h2 id="200">5. Check list item catalogue</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Work through the check list in order to review your settings for the item catalogue.</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>[&nbsp;]&nbsp;Did you create appropriate categories for your items?</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>[&nbsp;]&nbsp;Did you create description texts for all items?</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>[&nbsp;]&nbsp;Did you set the correct item availability levels?</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>[&nbsp;]&nbsp;Did you select the availability of all items you want to offer in your webshop?</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>[&nbsp;]&nbsp;Did you check that all prices are displayed correctly in the webshop?</p>
</li>
</ul>
